# =====================================================================
customUI.triggerVolumeEffectEditor.field.set_camera.Mode = Mode
customUI.triggerVolumeEffectEditor.field.set_camera.Mode.tooltip = Camera mode to apply: "first_person" — forces first-person view; "third_person" — forces third-person view; "reset" — restores the player's own camera preference and clears any lock.
